sentences.en: Secondly, opening up to the global market also puts pressure on Vietnamese producers to apply ICT in their business to gain competitiveness vis-à-vis their competitors.

sentences.en: The industry’s competitive disadvantages vis-à-vis other regional competitors due to local garment makers’ inability to locally source fabrics of the required specifications at competitive prices.
